<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title><%= title %> · Express Starter Lab</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />

    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #0f172a;
        --bg-card: #0b1220;
        --accent: #38bdf8;
        --accent-soft: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.12);
        --text: #e5e7eb;
        --text-muted: #9ca3af;
        --border: rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.25);
        --shadow-soft: 0 18px 45px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.75);
        --radius-xl: 18px;
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        min-height: 100vh;
        font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI",
          sans-serif;
        background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #1d283a 0, #020617 55%);
        color: var(--text);
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      .nav {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 16px 24px;
      }

      .nav-inner {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 1040px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 16px;
      }

      .nav-logo {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 0.03em;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--text-muted);
      }

      .nav-logo-badge {
        width: 24px;
        height: 24px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        border: 1px solid var(--accent-soft);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        color: var(--accent);
        background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 0, #0ea5e9 0, #020617 55%);
      }

      .nav-links {
        display: flex;
        gap: 18px;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }

      .nav-links a {
        color: var(--text-muted);
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 6px 10px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        border: 1px solid transparent;
        transition: all 0.18s ease-out;
      }

      .nav-links a:hover {
        color: var(--text);
        border-color: var(--border);
        background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.8);
      }

      .nav-links a.primary {
        color: var(--accent);
        border-color: var(--accent-soft);
        background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.9);
      }

      main {
        flex: 1;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 12px 16px 32px;
      }

      .shell {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 1040px;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 3fr);
        margin-top: 10px;
      }

      @media (min-width: 900px) {
        .shell {
          grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 3fr) minmax(0, 2fr);
          gap: 32px;
          align-items: stretch;
        }
      }

      .card {
        background: linear-gradient(
            to bottom right,
            rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.88),
            rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.98)
          );
        border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
        padding: 28px 26px 24px;
      }

      .card-header-kicker {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        padding: 4px 10px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        border: 1px solid var(--accent-soft);
        background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, #0ea5e9 0, #020617 65%);
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        color: #e0f2fe;
      }

      .card-header-kicker-dot {
        width: 7px;
        height: 7px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: #22c55e;
        box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.32);
      }

      h1 {
        margin: 18px 0 8px;
        font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 2.7vw, 2.4rem);
        letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      }

      .subtitle {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 0.98rem;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        max-width: 42rem;
      }

      .metrics-grid {
        display: grid;
        gap: 14px;
        margin-top: 22px;
      }

      @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .metrics-grid {
          grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
        }
      }

      .metric-card {
        border-radius: 14px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(51, 65, 85, 0.85);
        background: radial-gradient(
          circle at top left,
          rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.16),
          rgba(15, 23, 42, 1)
        );
        padding: 12px 14px;
      }

      .metric-label {
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.12em;
        color: #bae6fd;
        margin-bottom: 4px;
      }

      .metric-value {
        font-size: 1.05rem;
        font-weight: 500;
      }

      .metric-detail {
        margin-top: 3px;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        color: var(--text-muted);
      }

      .hint-line {
        margin-top: 18px;
        font-size: 0.8rem;
        color: var(--text-muted);
      }

      .hint-line code {
        font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Monaco, Consolas,
          "Liberation Mono", "Courier New", monospace;
        font-size: 0.78rem;
        background: #020617;
        padding: 3px 6px;
        border-radius: 6px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.4);
      }

      .card-secondary h2 {
        margin: 0 0 12px;
        font-size: 1.05rem;
      }

      .log-hint {
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: var(--text-muted);
        line-height: 1.5;
      }

      footer {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 10px 0 16px;
        font-size: 0.75rem;
        color: var(--text-muted);
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header class="nav">
      <div class="nav-inner">
        <div class="nav-logo">
          <div class="nav-logo-badge">ZT</div>
          <span>Zero-Trust Lab · Express Starter</span>
        </div>
        <nav class="nav-links">
          <a href="/">Home</a>
          <a href="/about">About</a>
          <a href="/status" class="primary">Status</a>
          <a href="/api/health">Health API</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main>
      <div class="shell">
        <section class="card">
          <div class="card-header-kicker">
            <span class="card-header-kicker-dot"></span>
            Runtime · Live application status
          </div>

          <h1>Application Status</h1>

          <p class="subtitle">
            This page shows live runtime information for the Express app running
            on EC2, including uptime, Node.js version, environment, and
            timestamp. Useful for quick smoke checks.
          </p>

          <div class="metrics-grid">
            <div class="metric-card">
              <div class="metric-label">Uptime</div>
              <div class="metric-value">
                <%= uptimeSeconds.toFixed(0) %> seconds
              </div>
              <div class="metric-detail">
                Time since the Node.js process started.
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="metric-card">
              <div class="metric-label">Node.js Version</div>
              <div class="metric-value"><%= nodeVersion %></div>
              <div class="metric-detail">
                Ensure this matches the version you expect (e.g. Node 20.x).
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="metric-card">
              <div class="metric-label">Environment</div>
              <div class="metric-value"><%= environment %></div>
              <div class="metric-detail">
                Typically <code>production</code> on EC2, or
                <code>development</code> locally.
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="metric-card">
              <div class="metric-label">Timestamp (UTC)</div>
              <div class="metric-value" style="font-size: 0.9rem;">
                <%= timestamp %>
              </div>
              <div class="metric-detail">
                ISO 8601 timestamp generated on each request.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <p class="hint-line">
            For a JSON-friendly health check, use
            <code>/api/health</code>. This status view is meant for humans, not
            machines.
          </p>
        </section>

        <aside class="card card-secondary">
          <h2>Operational hints</h2>
          <p class="log-hint">
            On the EC2 instance, you can inspect logs and service health using:
          </p>
          <p class="log-hint">
            <code>sudo systemctl status express-starter</code><br />
            <code>sudo journalctl -u express-starter -n 50 --no-pager</code>
          </p>
          <p class="log-hint">
            If you’re debugging Cloudflare Tunnel behaviour:
          </p>
          <p class="log-hint">
            <code>sudo systemctl status cloudflared</code><br />
            <code>sudo journalctl -u cloudflared -n 50 --no-pager</code>
          </p>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </main>

    <footer>
      Express Starter · Zero-Trust Lab · Powered by Node.js, AWS & Cloudflare
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
